<ref>{{Cite web | last = Corberly | first = Linda T. | coauthors = Paul Onderdonk, Gene C. Schaefr, et. al | title = Brief for the American Legion as ''Amici Curiae'' in Support of Petitioner | publisher = The American Legion | date = June 2010 | url = http://www.americanbar.org/content/dam/aba/publishing/preview/publiced_preview_briefs_pdfs_09_10_09_751_PetitionerAmCuAmericanLegion.authcheckdam.pdf | accessdate = 2013-05-28 | archive-date = 2012-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120118124850/http://www.americanbar.org/content/dam/aba/publishing/preview/publiced_preview_briefs_pdfs_09_10_09_751_PetitionerAmCuAmericanLegion.authcheckdam.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，約翰·馬歇爾的退伍軍人的法律支援中心和診所（John Marshall Veterans Legal Support Center and Clinic）
