== 法院意見 ==
[[File:File-Official_roberts_CJ_cropped.jpg|alt=]][[約翰·格洛佛·羅伯茨|約翰·羅伯茨]]撰寫[[主要意見書|主要意見書]]。]]
在8–1的判決（大法官的正反立場與2010年的{{link-en|美國訴史蒂文斯案|United States v. Stevens}}恰好相同）中<ref>{{Cite news | last = Singer | first = Sam | title = Previewing Phelps v. Snyder | work = The Daily Caller | date = 2010-10-05 | url = http://dailycaller.com/2010/10/05/previewing-phelps-v-snyder/ | accessdate = 2013-05-28 | archive-date = 2015-04-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150429095710/http://dailycaller.com/2010/10/05/previewing-phelps-v-snyder/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，最高法院作出有利於菲爾普斯的裁決，維持了第四巡迴法院的判決。首席大法官[[約翰·格洛佛·羅伯茨|約翰·羅伯茨]]（與「史蒂文斯」一案相同）撰寫主要意見書說明「在整個上下文中，威斯特布路說了什麼和在哪裡以什麼形式選擇說出來，都有權根據第一修正案受到『特殊保護』，且該保護不能因陪審團裁決糾察隊是離譜的而推翻」<ref name="geidner">{{Cite news|last=Geidner |first=Chris |title=Supreme Court Upholds Westboro Baptist Church Members' Right to Picket Funerals |work=Metro Weekly |date=2011-03-02 |url=http://www.metroweekly.com/poliglot/2011/03/supreme-court-upholds-westboro.html |accessdate=2013-05-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208053429/http://www.metroweekly.com/poliglot/2011/03/supreme-court-upholds-westboro.html |archivedate=2013-02-08 }}</ref>。

法院意見還說追悼會並沒有受到打擾，「威斯特布路很好地停留在遠離追悼會的地方，斯奈德頂多能看到糾察隊員標語的頂端，而且沒有任何跡象表明糾察隊本身干擾了追悼會」<ref>{{Cite news | last = Mears | first = Bill | title = Anti-gay church's right to protest at military funerals is upheld | work = CNN.com | date = 2011-03-02 | url = http://www.cnn.com/2011/US/03/02/scotus.westboro.church/index.html?iref=allsearch | accessdate = 2013-05-28 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045018/http://www.cnn.com/2011/US/03/02/scotus.westboro.church/index.html?iref=allsearch | dead-url = no }}</ref>。判決也拒絕擴充「受制而走不開的觀眾學說」，它說斯奈德並不是在受到脅迫的狀態下聽到負面的言論<ref name="gregory">{{Cite news | last = Gregory | first = Sean | title = Why the Supreme Court Ruled for Westboro | newspaper = Time Magazine | date = 2011-03-03 | url = http://www.time.com/time/nation/article/0,8599,2056613,00.html | accessdate = 2013-08-28 | archive-date = 2013-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130824004933/http://www.time.com/time/nation/article/0,8599,2056613,00.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

大法官[[史蒂芬·布雷耶|史蒂芬·布雷耶]]撰寫了一份[[協同意見書|協同意見書]]，強調他認為該判決只跟糾察隊有關，並不將威斯特布路浸信會攻擊斯奈德家族的線上發表考慮進去<ref>{{Cite news | last = Barnes | first = Robert | title = Supreme Court Rules First Amendment Protects Church's Right to Picket Funerals | work = Washington Post | date = 2011-03-03 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/03/02/AR2011030202548.html | accessdate = 2013-05-28 | archive-date = 2020-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201010054329/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/03/02/AR2011030202548.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

大法官[[塞繆爾·阿利托|塞繆爾·阿利托]]，如同在「史蒂文斯」一案中，是唯一一個在案件中發表反對意見的大法官，他的[[不同意見書|不同意見書]]以「我們國家對自由開放的辯論所作的全然承諾，不是在此案中發生的惡毒語言攻擊的許可證」作為開頭<ref name="geidner"/>。他結論，「為了有一個對公共議題可以公開激烈辯論的社會，沒有必要允許像上訴者那樣對無辜受害者的殘害行為」<ref name="gregory"/>。

在2011年7月的一場演講中，大法官金斯伯格（Ginsburg）稱阿利托的不同意見書非常「真誠（heart-felt）」，並說他「強調了斯奈德家族所遭受到的無與倫比的悲痛」，且指出「雖然沒有任何一位法院成員聯名，他的意見書與很多法院觀察家的觀點一致，其中包括國家最新的退休大法官史蒂文斯，〔他〕最近告訴聯邦律師協會說他『將會加入〔大法官阿利托的〕強而有力的不同意見書』」<ref>{{Cite web | last = Ginsburg | first = Ruth Bader | title = A Survey of the 2010 Term for presentation to the Otsego County Bar Association Cooperstown Country Club | publisher = United States Supreme Court | date = 2011-07-22 | url = http://www.supremecourt.gov/publicinfo/speeches/viewspeeches.aspx?Filename=sp_07-22-11.html | accessdate = 2013-05-28 | archive-date = 2014-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140703165441/http://www.supremecourt.gov/publicinfo/speeches/viewspeeches.aspx?Filename=sp_07-22-11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

